---
title: One-Pot Southwest-Style Sausage and Cavatappi with Monterey Jack and Baby Spinach
description: This one-and-done dinner in a hurry packs pork sausage, veggies and noodles into one easy bowl. What's even better? It's a meal that everyone is sure to devour!
